    "synopsis": "Talos and First Claw set in motion an audacious plan to throw an entire sector of the Imperium into chaos — but their visions of the future are about to converge with a reckoning they did not foresee. On the craftworld of Ulthwé, the Eldar farseers have read a great threat in the skein of fate, and they move to extinguish the Night Lords before prophecy can be fulfilled. As the alien hunters close in and old loyalties fracture, Talos returns to the haunted world of Tsagualsa for a final, brutal confrontation that brings the Prophet of the Eighth Legion's story to its end.",
